   20: -module(gb_sets_property_test_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   23: 
   24: -compile(export_all).
   25: -compile(nowarn_export_all).
   26: 
   27: all() -> [
   28:           add_case,
   29:           balance_case,
   30:           delete_case, delete_any_case,
   31:           difference_case,
   32:           from_ordset_case,
   33:           insert_case,
   34:           is_member_case,
   35:           iterator_case, iterator_from_case,
   36:           largest_case,
   37:           singleton_case,
   38:           smallest_case,
   39:           take_largest_case,
   40:           take_smallest_case
   41:     ].
   42: 
   43: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   44:     ct_property_test:init_per_suite(Config).
   45: 
   46: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   47:     Config.
   48: 
   49: add_case(Config) ->
   50:     do_proptest(prop_add, Config).
   51: 
   52: balance_case(Config) ->
   53:     do_proptest(prop_balance, Config).
   54: 
   55: delete_case(Config) ->
   56:     do_proptest(prop_delete, Config).
   57: 
   58: delete_any_case(Config) ->
   59:     do_proptest(prop_delete_any, Config).
   60: 
   61: difference_case(Config) ->
   62:     do_proptest(prop_difference, Config).
   63: 
   64: from_ordset_case(Config) ->
   65:     do_proptest(prop_from_ordset, Config).
   66: 
   67: insert_case(Config) ->
   68:     do_proptest(prop_insert, Config).
   69: 
   70: is_member_case(Config) ->
   71:     do_proptest(prop_is_member, Config).
   72: 
   73: iterator_case(Config) ->
   74:     do_proptest(prop_iterator, Config).
   75: 
   76: iterator_from_case(Config) ->
   77:     do_proptest(prop_iterator_from, Config).
   78: 
   79: largest_case(Config) ->
   80:     do_proptest(prop_largest, Config).
   81: 
   82: singleton_case(Config) ->
   83:     do_proptest(prop_singleton, Config).
   84: 
   85: smallest_case(Config) ->
   86:     do_proptest(prop_smallest, Config).
   87: 
   88: take_largest_case(Config) ->
   89:     do_proptest(prop_take_largest, Config).
   90: 
   91: take_smallest_case(Config) ->
   92:     do_proptest(prop_take_smallest, Config).
   93: 
   94: do_proptest(Prop, Config) ->
   95:     ct_property_test:quickcheck(
   96:         gb_sets_prop:Prop(),
   97:         Config).
